{"tid":762552,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"撞穿窿！潘燦良余香凝驚險扒龍舟","createTime":"2018-07-31T11:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T11:30:06.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2d1dc231c6db04a850c1682c5a7bdb9501e5227e","tid":762552,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T11:27:38.000Z","msg":"舞台劇演員潘燦良聯同導演陳詠燊出席電影《逆流大叔》新書分享會，與書迷分享拍攝點滴。問到可有難忘的場景？潘燦良表示：「有幕係要講我哋進行扒龍舟比賽，仲要我哋衝前兼轉彎，我坐頭排，余香凝就打鼓，真係同前面嗰隻船只有4呎咁近、好驚險，如果撞前面，第1個撞到余香凝，第2個就係我。」導演陳詠燊稱拍攝時都有叫演員小心撞到浮台，但最終浮台被撞穿窿，龍舟頭亦爛了。潘燦良則笑言因為練扒龍舟而練到手瓜起𦟌，他笑言：「嗰期真係大隻咗好多。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180729/mobile/bkn-20180729191536399-0729_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180729%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180729191536399-0729_00862_001.html&d=srOU00ChBn%2FrmsnY%2FJTeJzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=95701bc0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180729/mobile/bkn-20180729191536399-0729_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n又係余香凝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1187471577ffe9b2b3b0997189ed979fe22498a5","tid":762552,"uid":80015,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T11:28:36.000Z","msg":"導演真係慘, 拍完套野余香凝先搞單咁既野出黎"},{"pid":"4b99389191d05561f3222162424babe9e0bcd367","tid":762552,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1187471577ffe9b2b3b0997189ed979fe22498a5","tid":762552,"uid":80015,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T11:28:36.000Z","msg":"導演真係慘, 拍完套野余香凝先搞單咁既野出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T11:30:06.000Z","msg":"你太高估條女影響力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}